OL,5, A councillor has stepped down as deputy
OL,6, leader of the local authority after he 
OL,7, reportedly told a meeting that "all    
OL,8, Tories should be shot".                
OL,10,FIeuan Williams apologised for the      
OL,11,Fcomment, which the WalesOnline website 
OL,12,Fsaid was made at an internal Anglesey  
OL,13,Fcouncil meeting on Monday.             
OL,15,FThe independent councillor said he was 
OL,16,F"angry and emotional" about poverty    
OL,17,Fwhen he made the "crass remark".       
OL,19,FLocal Conservative MP Virginia Crosbie 
OL,20,Fsaid she was disgusted by the comment. 
